<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Lutz Tanner, Amtmann zu Neustadt an der Aisch</head><p>Der Rat teilt Unkenntnis wegen Feindschaft mit Tanners ehemaligem Diener Hans Puffer von Neuhof an der Zenn mit.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_521" id="260r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_521_r1l14">Lucʒen Tanner Amptman </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_521_r1l15">cʒu der Newenſtat an der Eyſche </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_521_r1l16"> <expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Lucʒ Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt von 
<del rend="strikethrough">Peter </del> Hanſen Puffers </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_521_r1l18">vvegen vom Newenhof 
<add><ab facs="#facs_521_r1l17">der ewr dıener geweſen iſt </ab></add> / vvıſʒen vvir cʒu der cʒeit nihts <expan>beſund<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_521_r1l20">daʒ vvir mit Jm cʒeſchicken <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vveſt Er aber 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>yemand<ex>en</ex></expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_521_r1l19">dheinen </ab></add> der <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_521_r1l21">dauor Er ſich beſorgt / 
<del rend="strikethrough">das </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_521_line_1576348586512_3673">den </ab></add> lieſʒt vns <expan>wiſʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> / ſo wolten wir den </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_521_r1l22">beſenden vnd ſein rede darümb hören / <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in <expan>vıg<ex>ilia</ex></expan> <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>ı</expan> <expan>Mich<ex>aelis</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_521" id="260r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Luczen Tanner, amptman czu der Newenstat an der
                                                Eysche</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Lucz, als ir uns
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt
                                                von Hansen Puffers wegen vom Newenhof, <add>der ewr
                                                  diener gewesen ist,</add> wiszen wir czu der czeit
                                                nihts <expan>besund<ex>er</ex>s,</expan> daz wir mit
                                                im cze schicken <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n;</expan> west
                                                er aber <add>dheinen</add> der
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, davor er sich
                                                besorgt, <add>den</add> lieszt uns
                                                  <expan>wisze<ex>n,</ex></expan> so wolten wir den
                                                besenden und sein rede darümb hören.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in
                                                  <expan>vig<ex>ilia</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan>
<expan>Mich<ex>aelis</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
